snippet.title: Esse Proxy - Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist today on Steam!  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1485070/Esse_Proxy
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/yNchrt4gpE

Slick, stylish and brutal, 3D Cyberpunk Shooter. Located in a dystopian future, you'll experience the intertwined stories of three different characters, each with their own abilities, playstyles, strengths and weaknesses. Kill or die, learn and repeat before you unveil the secrets of Esse Proxy.

OFFICIAL RELEASE DATE: June 23
